{"tid":2005234,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"烏茲別克中國建造水庫潰壩 淹沒民房近10萬人撤離","createTime":"2020-05-07T03:38:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T05:48:02.000Z","uid":54373,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e2b1d1e5e90cf513b1298ead061211ea98ee6f9a","tid":2005234,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:38:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images1.epochhk.com/pictures/150426/1-27@1200x1200.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages1.epochhk.com%2Fpictures%2F150426%2F1-27%401200x1200.jpg&h=2fbc8f20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n烏茲別克東部的薩爾多巴水庫（Sardoba Reservoir）29米高的混泥土壁中出現一道破口，大水朝兩側迅速漫溢，如海嘯般的大水淹沒數百座房屋。（影片截圖）<br />\n<br />\n2020年05月04日<br />\n位於中亞的內陸國家烏茲別克東部一座水庫，1日早晨發生潰壩事故，大水摧毀農田並淹沒數百座民房，促使烏茲別克及哈薩克當局撤離將近10萬人。<br />\n<br />\n事發在烏茲別克東部的薩爾多巴水庫（Sardoba Reservoir）29米高的混泥土壁中出現一道破口，大水朝兩側迅速漫溢，如海嘯般的大水淹沒數百座房屋。<br />\n<br />\n緊急情況部發言人薩迪科夫（Murod Sadikov）稍早表示，大水造成許多農地和住宅被淹沒，已知有56人受傷，救援仍在繼續，相關單位正努力將水流引導回河流或附近湖泊。<br />\n<br />\n烏茲別克當局疏散錫爾河流域22個村莊的民眾約7萬人。<br />\n<br />\n哈薩克總統托卡葉夫（Kassym-Jomart Tokayev）3日則在推特（Twitter）發文指出，靠近烏茲別克邊界的10座哈薩克村莊也遭受「嚴重洪患」，迫使哈薩克當局撤離2萬2000人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n烏茲別克當局3日稍早已經針對「官方疏失」和施工違規情事展開刑事調查。<br />\n<br />\n薩爾多巴水庫是2010年在時任總理、現任總統米爾濟約耶夫（Shavkat Mirziyoyev）的執掌下開始建造。<span style=\"color: red;\">當時烏茲別克政府與<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中國</span>簽訂一份2300萬美元的合約，準備在大壩上建設水力發電廠，預定於2022年完工。不過，水庫最終於2017年完工。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images1.epochhk.com/pictures/150425/2-9-600x347@1200x1200.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages1.epochhk.com%2Fpictures%2F150425%2F2-9-600x347%401200x1200.jpg&h=ae71492f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n烏茲別克東部的薩爾多巴水庫（Sardoba Reservoir）29米高的混泥土壁中出現一道破口，大水朝兩側迅速漫溢，如海嘯般的大水淹沒數百座房屋。（影片截圖）"},{"pid":"7bd0a698f090830b3968e90465b6606a3b96205d","tid":2005234,"uid":54373,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:39:42.000Z","msg":"2300萬美元就起到水庫+發電廠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個總統仲同佢簽約<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f42c4bc7b4dff642235c412d3fe4fd84c40c8e86","tid":2005234,"uid":52946,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:41:04.000Z","msg":"中國基建真係世界級 垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6964fd9eada3408585d6e26ddc83cb3ccf21f712","tid":2005234,"uid":168567,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:41:37.000Z","msg":"中國: 少左10萬人 咪多啲電用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"146fb667b09aeea8ff9671b832e7db3d6abef38a","tid":2005234,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:41:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18a5535a4ff0dc73d730a24a3df74fa9e360f9cc","tid":2005234,"uid":321977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:42:10.000Z","msg":"紙庫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a45bc8a37caecf09bd29ab6a1b1a1e5ec559a285","tid":2005234,"uid":63253,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:43:26.000Z","msg":"讉責左d水未"},{"pid":"26063992aead306d418a495a0bb39b3e2969a447","tid":2005234,"uid":19126,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:44:44.000Z","msg":"支那 :你可以再科水俾我地起過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj